me friends to join me in PVP but need to tell them what all the specific differences of each server are.  Any help would be greatly appreciated.<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufricka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fricka</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/shanks/teenyknot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/23/01 11:25:04 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/Sigs/9frickaface.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: list of differences?</span><hr size=1> It might be easier if ye told us what ye were looking for and we could recommend a server for ye.<br>
<br>
One of the positive things, in my opinion, about the PvP servers is that climates change.  Player made rules emerge and new styles of playing become more or less popular.<br>
<br>
For really detailed information I suggest ye go to each server's discussion board.  In general: Rallos= free for all within 4 levels, it is difficult at first to get through the lower levels.  There are folks there who play &quot;PK vs Anti-PK&quot;. Tallon and Vallon have folks who play &quot;good vs evil&quot; and folks who play &quot;pure team&quot;.  Vallon has the Safehouse-based guild, Shanks, who are all Barbarian and may have an edge on Tallon with the variety of pure team guilds out there.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> ALSO</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> a new server is coming up, your best bet may be to wait and see what it will be like and starting over there. <p><table border=0 align=left width=100%>
